==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cognize
<hw>Cog"nize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Cognizant</er>, <er>Recognize</er>.]</ety> <def>To know or perceive;
to recognize.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The reasoning faculty can deal with no facts until they are
<qex>cognized</qex> by it.</q> <rj><qau>H. Spencer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cognizee</ent>⟦br⟧
